    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-09-15T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-09-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="43" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d43">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-09-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 15, 1893</hi>
                        </date>.
                            (Received September 15.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Thompson transmits advices received by him to the effect that the
                        revolting squadron, with the apparent purpose of bombarding the city, has
                        ordered merchant vessels in the harbor to move far up the bay.</p>
            </div>
